Name: Kus Uçusu
Summary: A young fan maneuvers her way into a seasoned anchor's newsroom but soon confronts the dark side of ambition, envy and the desire to be seen.

Name: Sahsiyet
Summary: A man diagnosed with Alzheimer's decides to punish criminals.

Name: Yabani
Summary: The life of a young boy named Yaman growing up on the streets, along with his friends, as they face challenges of survival.

Name: Aile
Summary: Aile is a story of Aslan who is the son of a large family, runs a nightclub. An extremely shrewd man. He is a dark and mysterious character. Psychologist Devin will enter the life of this difficult man and it becomes intense.

Name: Gibi
Summary: Yilmaz and Ilkkan are two friends who are constantly fighting each other. Their greatest feature is always being able to do something that will turn their ordinary lives upside down.

Name: Sen Çal Kapimi
Summary: Due to circumstances, Serkan and Eda will have to pretend to be engaged. Comedy begins. And romance?

Name: Çukur
Summary: A dangerous neighborhood, "The Pit", ran by a noble mafia family called Koçovali. When the family is in the danger of losing the control of The Pit, their youngest son now must come back to his home, where he could never escape from.
Stars: Aras Bulut IynemliErkan Kolçak KöstendilRiza Kocaoglu

Name: Yali Çapkini
Summary: Halis Aga, the pillar of one of Gaziantep's well-established families, decides to marry off his unruly grandson Ferit to bring him into line.

Name: Kurulus: Osman
Summary: The series will focus on the life of Osman Bey, the son of Ertugrul Gazi and the founder of the Ottoman Empire.

Name: Atatürk 1881 - 1919
Summary: The life story of Veteran Mustafa Kemal Atatürk, the founding father of the Republic of Turkey and its first President, supreme commander of Turkish War of Independence, and revolutionary statesman.

Name: Yargi
Summary: Follows how a fearless lawyer and a renowned prosecutor meet during a crime investigation.

Name: Terzi
Summary: A famous tailor begins to sew a wedding dress for his best friend's fiance- but all three have dark secrets that will soon upend their lives.

Name: Hudutsuz Sevda
Summary: The series followed Halil Ibrahim as he seeks revenge for the death of the love of his life. His plans are derailed when he meets Zeynep from the Leto family.

Name: Kizilcik Serbeti
Summary: A love story between two extreme families with the same truth but different methods.

Name: Çekiç ve Gül: Bir Behzat Ç. Hikayesi
Summary: The story is a Turkish-made detective, drama, adventure, comedy, thriller and action internet series, inspired by Emrah Serbes' novel of the same name, Çekiç ve Gül.

Name: Ilk Ve Son
Summary: The story of Deniz and Baris' relationship for 10 years. The two young men who met in their mid 20's, until the day they divorced; a love story sometimes sunny, cloudy, stormy, possible and impossible.

Name: Kara Sevda
Summary: A young artist finds herself obligated to sacrifice her love story for hiding a family secret.

Name: The Protector
Summary: Discovering his ties to a secret ancient order, a young man living in modern Istanbul embarks on a quest to save the city from an immortal enemy.

Name: Bambaska Biri
Summary: The brutal murder of Hamdi Atilbay brings together the paths of young prosecutor Leyla, and a famous journalist Kenan. However, this murder is covered with facts that will also destroy their love.

Name: Kizil Goncalar
Summary: A mother and daughter flee to escape from a forced marriage in a restrictive sect. The mother works for a progressive psychiatrist whose daughter's identity causes turmoil, despite their growing bond.

Name: Siyah Beyaz Ask
Summary: A doctor who has devoted herself to healing others encounters a cold-blooded killer with a wounded past. What happens when the woman who saves lives is captured by the man who takes them?

Name: Adim Farah
Summary: Farah is a 28-year-old Iranian doctor who works illegally as a cleaner in Istanbul and witnesses a murder committed by the mafia.

Name: Ezel
Summary: Betrayed by his trusted friends and the woman he loved, Ömer Uçar returns as Ezel to exact his vengeance.

Name: Kurtlar Vadisi
Summary: Follows a Turkish agent working under the assumed identity of Polat Alemdar attempting to infiltrate the Turkish mafia.

Name: Ask-i Memnu
Summary: Rich Adnan marries Bihter, who is younger than him. A poisonous forbidden love begins between Adnan's nephew Behlül and Bihter who lives in the same mansion.

Name: Dirilis: Ertugrul
Summary: The heroic story of Ertugrul Ghazi, the father of Osman (Uthman) who founded the Ottoman Empire.

Name: Prens
Summary: Bongomia is a country that no one cares about, in a history that no one cares about. After the sudden and suspicious death of Thun, king of Bongomia, a complicated story begins when the Prince, whom no one takes seriously and whose family does not even bother to name, comes to the throne.
Stars: Giray AltinokDerya Pinar AkÇagdas Onur Öztürk

Name: Kiralik Ask
Summary: When Defne's brother gets into debt and is held captive, Defne is forced to accept an offer in exchange for the money. She has to make Omer, a wealthy shoe designer who owns a company, fall in love with her and marry her.

Name: Behzat Ç.: Bir Ankara Polisiyesi
Summary: An inharmonious police team in Ankara Police Force and its discredited police chief fight crime.

Name: Arak
Summary: In 1998, Elif Çinar, the wife of Rauf Çinar, one of the country's leading economics professors, is stabbed by a burglar named Necip Talan. The lives of these two families from completely different worlds change after that night.

Name: Leyla ile Mecnun
Summary: It is an unique and heartwarming show follows the extraordinary journey of a couple named Leyla and Mecnun. With Ali Atay portraying Mecnun and Ezgi Asaroglu as Leyla, the series has garnered a massive fan base and critical acclaim.

Name: Erkenci Kus
Summary: Famous photographer Can Divit returns to Istanbul to save his family's advertising agency from ruin. The only person he trusts there is Sanem, a young aspiring writer. She is not convinced in his honesty, but soon falls for his charm.

Name: Eskiya Dünyaya Hükümdar Olmaz
Summary: The series tells the life of Hizir Cakirbeyli. It has entered the realm of the mafia at a young age.

Name: Kulüp
Summary: In cosmopolitan 1950s Istanbul, a mother with a troubled past works at a nightclub to reconnect with and help the rebellious daughter she couldn't raise.

Name: Kara Para Ask
Summary: Omar is a police officer. After the death of his fiancé he suffers great pain. Sibel, Omar's fiancée's body was found on the top of a cliff, in a car next to a fairly old, rich business man. After the shock of her sudden death and the accusations of his love cheating on him, Omar realizes that there is more behind her suspicious murder.

Name: Sandik Kokusu
Summary: It is a hopeful story of a family starting over in Adana and extending to Istanbul, with an impressive atmosphere.

Name: Muhtesem Yüzyil: Kösem
Summary: Anastasia a young Greek woman in Ahmed I's harem takes on the name 'Kosem' (leader, pioneer). In a world of men, she rules of the Ottoman Empire through her sons and grandson.

Name: Sahmaran
Summary: When Sahsu goes to Adana for a lecture, it's the perfect chance to face her estranged grandfather. But soon, she finds herself in the midst of a legend.

Name: Kudüs Fatihi Selahaddin Eyyubi
Summary: The life of Muslim ruler Saladin and he conquered Jerusalem. Furthermore, it focuses on his battles against the Crusaders and his goal to unite the Muslim territories of Syria, northern Mesopotamia, Palestine and Egypt under his rule.

Name: Günesi Beklerken
Summary: Looking for a better life, Demet tries to convince her only daughter Zeynep to leave their home village. They move into Demet's old friend's house Jale, and Zeynep is able to enroll at the same private college as where Jale works as the principal.

Name: Muhtesem Yüzyil
Summary: From 1520, follows Suleiman the Magnificent and his relatives from his great conquests to the "Battle of Szigeth".

Name: Içerde
Summary: A story of two brothers torn from each other. Now on the opposite sides of the law, brothers Sarp and Mert are put against each other, unaware of their fraternity.

Name: Hercai
Summary: Miran is seeking revenge for his parents death so he plans to marry daughter Reyyan from the family who were responsible for that. Unexpectedly he falls in love with Reyyan. Will this change the plan?

Name: Biz Kimden Kaçiyorduk Anne?
Summary: Hiding a mysterious past, a mother lives like a nameless fugitive with her daughter as they make hotels their home and see everyone else as a threat.

Name: Vatanim Sensin
Summary: During the occupation of Izmir by the Greeks, a Turkish soldier starts to work for the enemy. But he is not really on the side of the enemy. He must keep this secret at the cost of losing his family.

Name: Yasak Elma
Summary: Three things in life can not be hidden "love, smoke and lack of money". The social society and the events behind the business world are told.

Name: Zeytin Agaci
Summary: Three close friends set off on a journey to Ayvalik and then to their reshaped future.

Name: Ayak Isleri
Summary: Experienced missionary Vedat and philosophy-educated, politically correct Evren are the duo assigned to the 'extremely important' errands of a wealthy businessman. This discordant duo, one of whom closes his eyes and does his duty, questions his name, embarks on another adventure. But more they conflict within themselves than they do on duty.

Name: Safir
Summary: Yaman and Feraye, who have kept a great love hidden from everyone since childhood, have very little time left before they are reunited again.

Name: Ask 101
Summary: In 1990s Turkey, a group of teenage outcasts band together to make their beloved teacher fall in love so she'll have a reason to stay in town with them.

Name: Kurtlar Vadisi: Pusu
Summary: Valley of the Wolves, the legendary action drama, centers around Polat Alemdar and follows his journey to serve his country by trying to uncover the truth and defeating the secret enemies aka the controllers of the global power.

Name: Sakla Beni
Summary: An encounter between Incila, Naz's despised assistant and Mete begins to change the direction of Naz's future, where she plans everything with Mete with a toxic passion.

Name: Fi
Summary: The story of those who pursue passion, those who fly at the expense of burning and those who stand up against life in pain.

Name: Destan
Summary: The epic love story of Akkiz, a warrior mountain girl, and disabled Prince Batuga, who were both orphaned by Gök Han in the 8th century in the harsh steppes of Central Asia.

Name: Aynen Aynen
Summary: The series tells the story of Deniz and Nil's entertaining relationship by explaining the relationship between men and women in a humorous as well as realistic language. We see the situations in which Nil and Deniz want to show themselves to the other party in the relationship and in fact their own real thoughts.

Name: Ya Çok Seversen
Summary: Ates was sent to boarding school after his mother's death and never returned home. He trusts no one. Leyla, on the other hand, has never known her family and earns money by cheating. What will happen when they cross paths?

Name: Mucize Doktor
Summary: A distinguished surgical unit turns upside down when a strange new resident joins the team. Ali has Savant syndrome, making it hard for him to communicate with other people, even though he is a phenomenal doctor.

Name: Kübra
Summary: Follows Gökhan Ahinolu, whose connection with his girlfriend is strained after he gets a message from a user named Kübra. Everything will alter due to this communication, and something unexpected will happen.

Name: Atiye
Summary: A painter in Istanbul embarks on a personal journey as she unearths universal secrets about an Anatolian archaeological site and its link to her past.

Name: Son Yaz
Summary: Idealist Public Prosecutor Selim receives an offer he cannot refuse from organized crime leader Selcuk Taskin, whom he sent to prison. Selcuk will testify in the prosecutor's case, but in return, he asks the prosecutor to protect his son.

Name: Yakamoz S-245
Summary: After disaster strikes Earth, a marine biologist on a submarine research mission must fight to survive with the crew as a conspiracy comes to light.

Name: Kuzgun
Summary: Kuzgun's family life changes completely as a result of the caliper held against his father, who is a police. Kuzgun will fall into a bondage, pain, anger, and struggle that will last 20 years.

Name: Ask Mantik Intikam
Summary: A couple gets divorced after several years of marriage. After that, the man suddenly gets rich, and life changes again when his ex-wife starts working with him.

Name: Dogu
Summary: Dogu is a young man who is not successful in anything. The dream of Dogu, which is not supported by anyone, is to be a comedian. He strives to make his dream come true.

Name: Alparslan: Büyük Selçuklu
Summary: The TRT production is a prequel story of Awakening: the Great Seljuk. It depicts the life and triumphs of Sultan Alparslan, the second sultan of the Seljuk dynasty, whose victories expanded the empire in the 11th century.

Name: Kardeslerim
Summary: 4 siblings have to struggle with life after their parents' death.

Name: Muhtesem Ikili
Summary: Muhtesem Ikili is an adaption of the famous American movie, Tango and Cash. A story of two police officer Mert Barca and Mustafa Kerim Can / MKC. Barca and MKC, are forced to come together for a drug operation.

Name: Seref Meselesi
Summary: Follow the Kilic brothers as they take different paths in life after moving from the tiny Ayvalik to the vibrant Istanbul.

Name: Bir Derdim Var
Summary: Dr. Nilüfer is constantly pursuing a secret that could jeopardize her work, which will lead to a major conflict with the inflexible prosecutor Ömer (Mert Firat).

Name: Günesin Kizlari
Summary: Gunes is a 35 years old woman and a literature teacher whose husband left her with no reason. So she decides to get married in order to afford a good future for her three daughters.

Name: Çarpisma
Summary: It is about life that intersects with the collision of four cars.

Name: Sila
Summary: A young woman's forced marriage to the agha of a tribe in Southeastern Turkey leads to tragedy and social change.

Name: Kadin
Summary: Bahar, a loving mother who struggles to maintain a life with her two children, must deal with life's challenges and uncover the hidden truths of the past.

Name: Sadakatsiz
Summary: Asya is a successful doctor who has the perfect life with her husband and son. But after she finds a blonde hair on her husband's scarf, she discovers his extramarital affair and everything changes.

Name: Gülcemal
Summary: Abandoned by his mother as a boy. A man years later vows to get revenge on the mom and her new family all while unknowingly falling in love with her adopted daughter.

Name: Ask Laftan Anlamaz
Summary: Hayat is a country girl with strict parents. She is in a love hate relationship with her boss Murat. Hayat is full of secrets that can ruin her career and relationship.

Name: Duy Beni
Summary: Disadvantaged students earn scholarships to matriculate at a privileged kids' high school to investigate an accident that left their best friend paralyzed. They confront prejudice and intrigue, unsure of who is friend, foe, or culprit.

Name: Bu Sehir Arkandan Gelecek
Summary: Rauf, who is working as a cook on cargo ships, adopts and raises Ali who witnessed his mother's death when he was 5 years old. They work on ships for 24 years together. Rauf was both mother and father to Ali and has devoted his life to Ali to help him forget the trauma he had endured. With the support of Rauf, whom he calls "Mother", Ali gets maritime training.

Name: Poyraz Karayel
Summary: A defamed ex-cop, who is struggling to get back his son, is put on undercover duty within the biggest mafia in Istanbul.

Name: Hekimoglu
Summary: An antisocial maverick doctor who specializes in diagnostic medicine does whatever it takes to solve puzzling cases that come his way using his crack team of doctors and his wits.

Name: Marasli
Summary: Marasli (BurakDeniz) is a retired soldier turned bookstore owner. For Marasli, life changed drastically after his daughter is shot. One day, the beautiful Mahur (AlinaBoz) enters Marasli's bookstore and on that same day, she involuntarily gets involved in an incident. Marasli saves Mahur's life and from that day onwards, their fates will be linked.

Name: Sahane Hayatim
Summary: Full of intrigue, love, and emotion, Sebnem's unsettling life of being born with great injustices, working hard to overcome them, doing what was necessary to do so, and now trying to rid herself of her criminal past.

Name: Bozkir
Summary: In his profession, experienced captain Seyfi and rookie policeman Nuri Pamir face a child murder in the city. This murder leads them to the city's populated business man Abbas and his daughter Dilara.

Name: Ramo
Summary: The series will focus on the conflict between the two families and a great love that will flourish between this struggle.

Name: Kan Çiçekleri
Summary: Dilan and Baran are forced to marry to end a feud and save their brother, but their uncle wants to rekindle it. This conflict-filled relationship will bring strong winds between two hearts, but will it turn into a real marriage?

Name: Rumi
Summary: In 13th century Anatolia, as the Mongol threat looms and internal turmoil rages, Rumi, a wise spiritual figure, emerges to assuage people's fears. His timeless words unite reason and compassion, inspiring change.

Name: Pera Palas'ta Gece Yarisi
Summary: At a historic Istanbul hotel, a journalist is thrust into the past and must stop a plot that could change the fate of modern Turkey.

Name: Teskilat
Summary: National Intelligence Organization members are always ready to serve to destroy the enemies of Turkey.

Name: Bir Baskadir
Summary: A group of unique characters from dramatically different socio-cultural backgrounds meeting in startling circumstances in the vibrant and colorful city of Istanbul, - some by chance and some by force of will.

Name: Dolunay
Summary: Ferit, a rich and powerful man who has lost all faith in love, unknowingly hires Nazli, a girl who is bright and full of life, as domestic help. Their lives get complicated as she helps him fight for the custody of his orphaned nephew.

Name: Altin Kafes
Summary: The love story of Onur, the heir of the Beyoglu family, one of the richest people in the country, and the idealist Zeynep, who is a teacher at the family's school, for which they will pay a high price.

Name: Menajerimi Ara
Summary: At a talent agency in Istanbul, agents scramble to keep their star clients happy and their business afloat. The agents will juggle one situation to another in circumstances that blend their personal and professional lives.

Name: Tatli Küçük Yalancilar
Summary: Turkish remake of Pretty Little Liars.

Name: Mezarlik
Summary: "Graveyard" is a dark basement, where a special unit works to solve unsolved murders of women. Commissioner Önem, will have to fight masculine prejudices that support male violence.

Name: Ates Kuslari
Summary: Most street children do not reach the age of twenty. It cannot be said that those who saw it have lived. Drugs, violence, sexual harassment, starvation - the fate of street children is jail or the grave.

Name: Zemheri
Summary: Firuze and Ayaz. Two beautiful heart, two family carrying children overhead. Fate brought them together. Her father's unjust conviction in the elevator accident that killed thirteen people triggered Firuze. Carrying the responsibility of being the man of the house, Ayaz is faced with Firuze, which he sacrificed for his mother when he was about to marry another.

Name: Kaçis
Summary: War photographer Mehmet and a group of journalists visit an Ezidi village to conduct an investigation. The group, secretly crossing the border, falls into the hands of a radical terrorist organization as a result of a raid.

Name: Fatmagül'ün Suçu Ne?
Summary: Fatmagul, a simple happy village girl, is violated by 4 drunk rich young men, the extreme hardship she faces forced to marry a rapist and the great remorse felt by others for their inaction when innocence was violated forms the story.

Name: Kraliçe
Summary: Ates, one of the most famous basketball players in the country, and his wife Deniz are happily married. As Ates's name gets involved in a big scandal, their lives are turned upside down.

Name: Saygi
Summary: Saygi is spin off series of "Behzat C". The path of Ercüment, who seeks the solution of the corruption in the society by providing his own justice, will intersect with the two young people, who he believes act with the same purpose.

Name: Bir Ada Masali
Summary: The paths of city businesswoman Haziran and Poyraz, a handsome and helpful young man, intersect on Swallow Island, and love arises from the disagreements of these two opposite characters.

Name: Mahkum
Summary: Successful prosecutor Firat, who does not remember anything, is accused of murdering his wife and daughter. He has to escape from prison to reveal the truth.

Name: Öyle Bir Geçer Zaman ki
Summary: Set in the 1960, the series follows the dramatic changes to the lives of the Akarsu family after the patriarch's extra marital affair.
Stars: Ayça BingölYildiz Çagri AtiksoyAras Bulut Iynemli

Name: Aktris
Summary: The story of Turkey's most famous actress, who lives a bright life during the day and transitions to a dark world at night.

Name: Medcezir
Summary: Yaman,who lives in one of the Istanbul's suburbs,is arrested and put in jail along with his brother Kenan for his brother stole a car at a gas station.Yaman gets a chance for a brand new start when he meets a lawyer Selim who takes Yaman to his new home.

Name: Var Bunlar
Summary: The fun adventures of two close friends who are dragged into the inextricable monotony of daily life.

Name: Avrupa Yakasi
Summary: The life and times of the rather traditional Sutcuoglu family and their comedic struggles to adapt the high-profile contemporary life of Nisantasi.

Name: Bir Zamanlar Çukurova
Summary: A young couple who dreams of marriage conceal their identity to escape from the darned. They will introduce themselves as sibling and work in the farm in Adana.

Name: Bizim Hikaye
Summary: Filiznha has been struggling to survive in one of the city's slums, she is the eldest daughter of the family and has been taking care of her five younger siblings since their mother left them and their father is addicted to alcohol.

Name: Esaret
Summary: Orhun, the heir apparent of the Demirhanli family, will take their place on the screen with the vengeful love of Hira. Orhun, who punished the perpetrators, will now be guided by the fire of revenge in his heart.

Name: Kirli Sepeti
Summary: The lives of Istanbul's richest and most powerful families. Their maids, who are exposed to the secrets, mysteries and crimes hidden behind the closed doors of these houses, often become a part of them.

Name: Ömer
Summary: Ömer's life is turned upside down when he falls in love with Gamze - a relationship that his conservative father would never approve of.

Name: Karagül
Summary: After her husband's death, Ebru has to go to her husband's hometown due to financial problems. Will Ebru find out that she is living in a big lie about her son, whom she thought was dead?

Name: Ariza
Summary: Ali Riza is a taxi driver preparing to marry his sister Nihan off to his dear friend; Halide Gurkan attends Fuat Ersoylu's magnificent party given on the occasion of his father's birthday and during the party Fuat's son Burak proposes to Halide, who refuses, then leaves the party and gets into Ali Riza's taxi.
Stars: Tolga SaritasAyça Aysin TuranAhmet Mümtaz Taylan

Name: Alef
Summary: Two detectives try to unravel the mystery of the murders that followed the discovery of a body in the Bosphorus.

Name: Magarsus
Summary: It centers on the struggle of the Kurak family, which trades in citrus fruits in Saribahce, both with each other and with foreign powers that want dominance in the region.

Name: Sol Yanim
Summary: The drama series follows the story of a mother and her young daughter, Serra, as they try to get used to their new life in an ordinary neighborhood after falling from grace.

Name: Cesur Ve Güzel
Summary: Cesur returns to his father's village with an elaborate plan to avenge the death of his father. The only thing he hadn't planned for is Suhan, the daughter of the man he believes is responsible for his father's murder.

Name: Kasaba Doktoru
Summary: The talented and promising Ömer, who decided to become a doctor after losing his father, and the legendary surgeon Hakan, who is dedicated to saving lives, cross paths in a town hospital far from the city.

Name: Baht Oyunu
Summary: Ada grew up among women who believe they will be happy marrying the first men with whom they fall in love. But when her love interest Rüzgar abandons her, a challenging, romantic journey between love and destiny awaits her.

Name: Erkek Severse
Summary: Zeynep who lives with her twin children, is divorced from Oktay whom she married with great love during her university years, because she was cheated on. Zeynep loses her faith in men and closes her heart to love. Until he met Kenan Yelda.

Name: Sefirin Kizi
Summary: Sancar has always & Nare has always yearned for love. When they meet and fall in love as children, they know they are meant to be; they just have to wait to be old enough to marry. On the night of their wedding, a startling revelation by Nare forever changes their lives and puts their love on hold until the night of another wedding many years later.

Name: Ruhun Duymaz
Summary: An agent who sees nothing but his job with the eyes of honor; Ece, on the other hand, is a dazzling professional thief with a thousand and one skills.

Name: Kuzey Güney
Summary: Kuzey and Güney are brothers, yet they cannot be more different, both in character and also in their perception, much like their names they are north and south. While the older brother Güney strives in school and is the general good boy next door, his younger brother is nothing like him, he is wild and unpredictable.

Name: Kendi Düsen Aglamaz
Summary: Alize, who lost her mother the day she was born, is a beautiful but very selfish young girl. Alize, who goes crazy when she learns that her father is getting remarried, decides to fake a marriage with a man in order to take revenge.

Name: Elimi birakma
Summary: The story revolves around a girl named Azra who is studying abroad in America to become a professional cook just like her father.

Name: Yarim Kalan Asklar
Summary: Yarım Kalan Aşklar tells the story of Ozan, who died after a traffic accident and returned to the world in the body of a surprised person.

Name: Söz
Summary: Yavuz, a well-trained Turkish soldier, is in Istanbul with his fiance where a terrorist operation takes place. Bahar, who is not a surgeon, tries to save his fiance. After this incident, Yavuz goes back to Karabayir and Bahar follows him all the way to give him something that belongs to him.

Name: Senden Daha Güzel
Summary: Follows a doctor named Efsun, from Antep, as both her professional and love life are put to the test.

Name: Yesilçam
Summary: Showcasing Turkey of the 1960s, while it follows a film producer who will tell the story of survival in Yesilcam as he experiences the golden age of Turkish cinema.

Name: Ersan Kuneri
Summary: This is spin off comedy series of surreal film series "G.O.R.A".

Name: Halka
Summary: Two different young men coming together from different places stand side by side and fight against a conspiracy. They go after a past that doesn't leave behind. They bring to account of old notebooks, dirty cases, big and small lies. They're in a life with the Mafia, money, intrigue. They face against Halka, the terrifying face of which they have yet to know.

Name: Bay Yanlis
Summary: Wealthy restaurant owner Özgür prefers casual dating to serious relationships. Ezgi wants to get married, but she only ends up being used by men. Özgür agrees to give her dating tips so her next relationship with Serdar would work out.

Name: Emanet
Summary: Kevser grew up in a humble and poor neighborhood and after she becomes the bride of the son of the wealthy Kirimli family, her father cuts all ties with her as he does not approve of this marriage.
Stars: Halil Ibrahim CeyhanBerat Rüzgar ÖzkanÖmer Gecü

Name: Üç Kurus
Summary: When a serial killer stalks a Romani neighborhood, a hardboiled police captain teams up with a Gypsy crime boss to bring the killer to justice.

Name: Ben Bu Cihana Sigmazam
Summary: Cezayir decides to avenge his brother, who worked for the state and was victim of sabotage, begins a new life by faking his death but after a while he must return to his past life.

Name: Sarmasik Zamani
Summary: A murder had been committed in Eden Garden Estate, no one could believe it. Because on this site, people lived a quiet, calm and luxurious life. The residents of the site were known either for their fame through their professions or for their wealth directly from the family. No one had big troubles or fights in life. As it was, they lived an honest life... Until a wom... Read all

Name: Dogdugun Ev Kaderindir
Summary: The house where you were born even decides who you love and who you marry. First the mothers take the pen in his hand and start writing.

Name: Uyanis: Büyük Selcuklu
Summary: The war of the Great Seljuk Emperor, Meliksah and her loyalist, Sencer against Hasan Sabbah, who is sworn to destroy the Seljuks.

Name: Dilek Tasi
Summary: A very wealthy family in the 1980s is forced to adopt the daughter of man who is on trial with the death penalty.

Name: Afili Ask
Summary: Slanderous accusations force Ayse to marry Kerem, a well-known, rich, handsome playboy.

Name: Kördügüm
Summary: Ali Nejat Karasu is a former race-driver and a playboy turned into a businessman. He runs Karas Holdings which is part of a group his father built while making a fortune in ship building. His real passion is still cars and he dreams of launching a new car. While on business trip in Italy with his friend Ayhan, they come across Naz.

Name: Merhamet
Summary: A successful lawyer meets her lost childhood love after 13 years of deserting her poor hometown and abusive family. That encounter forces her to reconcile with her traumatic past and search for her lost family and their tragic fate.

Name: Aldatmak
Summary: He is a distinguished, respected family court judge. She is an honest and principled woman who has saved many marriages from destruction, made sure that many children receive the affection and love they deserve, and has always been on the side of justice.

Name: Camdaki Kiz
Summary: Nalan, who seems perfect from the outside, is being severely abused by her mother. Sedat, one of the richest men in Turkey, proposes to her. But her husband and family, who seem perfect from the outside, are not normal either.

Name: Kurt Seyit ve Sura
Summary: The love story of Kurt Seyit, a Crimean Tatar army major, and Sura, a rich Russian woman during the Russian Revolution and in the last days of the Ottoman Empire.

Name: Bir Küçük Gün Isigi
Summary: Sometimes the bad happen to make way for the good. (Destiny)

Name: Tuzak
